Authors: Ragui Halim and Brennan Fradelis

This is the latest version, version 1.0, of our AI Checkers Robot.
The "src" directory contains the AI player, the machine vision, and the arm controller code.

To install, please go to the "src" directory and type make. 
To start the Robot, please type ./checkers.

Please refer to the Poster in the "doc" directory to get a better understanding of our project.
		
This version is released on March 13, 2019. 